text: City, University of London is a public research university in London, United Kingdom, and a member institution of the federal University of London. It was founded in 1894. City joined the federal University of London on 1 September 2016. It then became part of the eighteen colleges and ten research institutes that then made up that university. ==References== Category:1890s establishments in England Category:1894 establishments in the United Kingdom Category:University of London
